{"tid":2199314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張宇人：與張竹君對於除戴口罩理解或有誤會","createTime":"2020-09-12T06:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T08:52:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa44d189ecf2b8a1b80c4a42fa507d127f9b7a5","tid":2199314,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、飲食界立法會議員張宇人，回應衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，「除下戴下口罩比不戴口罩」更高風險的說法，指雙方可能有誤解，澄清業界是建議客人在聊天時戴口罩，如果喝酒期間很頻密地不停除下口罩，當然是沒有意思，反問「又除又戴口罩」與直接不戴口罩，哪一樣風險更高，若果專家覺得「又除又戴口罩」較高風險，業界就不推行。<br />\n<br />\n衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君日前評論，政府若重開酒吧，顧客不斷拉低口罩飲酒，比不戴口罩更高危，被張宇人不點名批評「不要扮專家」。張竹君昨日表示，自己並非戴口罩的專家，但不要觸摸口罩的外面，以及摸完要立即洗手是常識。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356884\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2356884&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=ce087997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2356884</a>"},{"pid":"a782984e863486ad56aa405adabbaec3f3c59094","tid":2199314,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021e0137984fb83a1488506c3d7dcc86e951c37c","tid":2199314,"uid":16029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"政府唔鬧鬧佢？<br />\n咁耐以黎來係邊個死都唔開堂食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e140bee5900216ebd87ba0d6c3b93e1e6923ee","tid":2199314,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T06:05:49.000Z","msg":"廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e49c29a73037e6468e6426b7726731890364d7e","tid":2199314,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"021e0137984fb83a1488506c3d7dcc86e951c37c"